title: United Kingdom Imports - Meat, Fish & Crustaceans & Aquatics Prepared
description: Imports - Meat, Fish & Crustaceans & Aquatics Prepared in the United Kingdom increased to 365.67 GBP Million in September from 342.82 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports - Meat, Fish & Crustaceans & Aquatics Prep in the United Kingdom averaged 203.98 GBP Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 365.67 GBP Million in September of 2022 and a record low of 60.64 GBP Million in February of 2000. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Meat, Fish & Crustaceans & Aquatics Pr.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
